  "texts": [
    "A self-help book used to fend off depression, for example, is a mood-regulating artifact.",
    "A punching ball may instead count as an emotion-regulating artifact, if we use it to discharge our rage.",
    "Viola (2021) offers a different taxonomy, based on the component of emotive phenomena that is regulated.",
    "He thus describes feeling, evaluative, and motivational artifacts.",
    "According to this taxonomy, the self-help book could be characterized as an evaluative artifact, insofar as it allows its user to re-evaluate their relation to the world in a more positive light."
